fhb_base<- gsheet2tbl(
  "https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Kh0474vS9xCxwud6RSZgr7VeWEF7FAnYDSi3EMb_bYs/edit#gid=0", sheetid = "data-prod")

fhb_base <- fhb_base %>% 
  filter(state!="Uruguai") %>% 
  filter(trial != 11) %>% 
  filter(trial != 57)

fhb_base %>% 
  group_by(trial)
length(unique(fhb_base$trial))

Selecting fungicides

We selected four mixtures (QoI+DMI) and a single DMI with ate least 50 entries

# At least 50 entries
target <- c("check-0", "Azoxistrobina + Tebuconazole-2", "Piraclostrobina + Metconazole-2", "Tebuconazole-2", "Trifloxistrobina + Protioconazole-2", "Trifloxistrobina + Tebuconazole-2", "Piraclostrobina + Metconazole-1") 
fhb2 <- fhb_base %>%
  group_by(trial, AI) %>% 
  mutate(AI2 = paste(AI, n_spray, sep = "-")) %>% 
  filter(AI2 %in% target)

fhb2 %>%
  tabyl(AI2, n_spray)
fhb2 %>%
  tabyl(AI2, year)
fhb2 %>%
  tabyl(AI2)
fhb2 %>%
  tabyl(location)
fhb2 %>%
  tabyl(state)
fhb2 %>%
  tabyl(publication)

Create datasets

Severity Index

dat_sev <- fhb2 %>%
  select(1:12, 21, 25:32, 35:38) %>%
  group_by(trial, year, location, state, cultivar, reaction, n, AI, n_spray, yld_check, sev_check, mean_sev, publication, author, cons_group, AI2) %>%
  summarise(
    sev = mean(sev),
    V_sev = mean(V_sev)) %>% 
  filter(sev != "NA") %>% 
  filter(sev > 0) %>% 
  group_by(trial) %>% 
  mutate(n2 = n()) %>% 
  filter(n2 != 1)

dat_sev %>%
  tabyl(AI2, n_spray)
library(readr)
write_csv(dat_sev, "data/dat-sev.csv")

Yield

dat_yld <- fhb2 %>%
  select(1:12, 21, 25:32, 35:38) %>%
  group_by(trial, year, location, state, cultivar, reaction, n, AI, n_spray, yld_check, sev_check, mean_sev, publication, author, cons_group, AI2) %>%
  summarise(
    yld = mean(yld),
    V_yld = mean(V_yld)) %>% 
  filter(yld != "NA") %>% 
  group_by(trial) %>% 
  mutate(n2 = n()) %>% 
  filter(n2 != 1)

dat_yld %>%
  tabyl(AI2, n_spray)
library(readr)
write_csv(dat_yld, "data/dat-yld.csv")
